Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新驾驶员第一候补 水镜美三香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体潜能为特A++
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化现象的耐力值也是首位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体能力是驾驶员课程里首个M1水准的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 和一骑你相当哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二候补 御门零央
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体能A 格斗技能特A++
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技能等级连战术部队也自叹不如
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定连一骑都不一定能一招赢他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三候补 镝木彗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体能B 技能A
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况判断能力 特A++
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考能力 集中力 精神潜能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是历代驾驶员中最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑可是总士水准的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是全统括系统的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因子造成的影响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为提高生存概率而进行的基因操作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都正常显现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会出现无法理解自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而丧失身心协调的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提升自己能力的是其本人的意识和努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真正的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为原王牌你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…他们关系好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎经常在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就挺好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是考虑团队合作的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点还要看演习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能马上开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要来哦 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让他们能平安归来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须竭尽所能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来给他们做医学检查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要老师和咲良负责驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要为他们提供最好的后援
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始 你们就是岛的护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是打倒敌人的利剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三改良型诺顿模型AA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:24.18,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(682,663)}Nothung
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以十一号机、六号机、五号机为原型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.99,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,663)}Mk.Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.99,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(622,663)}Sechs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:27.99,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(781,663)}Funf
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是属于你们的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要个帅气的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还是暂定 就告诉你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分别是十一号机改 「魔雾」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.07,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(811,663)}Feth Fiada
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六号机改 「复仇者」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.74,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(726,663)}Fragarach
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五号机改 「命运石」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.26,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(731,663)}Lia Fail
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从我的故乡爱尔兰的神话里取的名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fe…好难叫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想改个名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位 这只是暂定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡诺恩老师一定会给我们想个更好的名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要粉色的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太喜欢黑色…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将机体视作自身就能产生一体感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 颜色和名字都很重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这个…说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会考虑你们的要求的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你们需要学习机体相关知识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner的特征是无需操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借由尼伯龙根系统连结驾驶员的脑部与机体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以思考来驾驶机体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 由于内置结晶核的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员会发生同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 由于痛觉对人类运动功能有重要作用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体损伤会转化为驾驶员的痛觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 满分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完 完全正确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个重点是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部分驾驶员会产生心理变化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入名为变性意识的状态…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小彗你太多话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这位原王牌驾驶员给大家打打气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没什么要说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位都要听大家的指示哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不合意的命令也可以不听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以才怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际作战和演习中 想法都会有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有许多你们不能接受的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 没有任何人会希望你们去死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都相信你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们也能相信大家去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 要是不能相信也没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要光着走过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会给人看见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人看啦 径直走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶服会缓和连接的冲击和同化现象…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一股汗臭！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镝木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 里奈学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样戴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 学会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到齐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 广登学长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 多关照啦 第三代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上那头盔就会鼓起勇气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 这片海打不到什么鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令和远见医生找你
