Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始实地训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香可是我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了故乡 我只剩那孩子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有子姐 我们理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说战斗生还率现在是史上最高值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次也全员生还了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争中没有绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们会提供最大限度的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要让孩子来保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就是Fafner Fafner就是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此之间要用机体名相称
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「魔雾」「复仇者」「命运石」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那么奇怪的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 卡诺恩学姐明明说起好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧 一定起出让你们接受的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了 数据我看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解体不顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要处理掉Nicht Sein也会停止共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以驾驶了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sein的处理可是早就定了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它本来是应该保留的最强机体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是侵蚀一骑身体的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Fafner的本质 卡诺恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令 有出击命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是给你的 镝木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼新先生似乎也安定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娶了晶晶小姐那样的大美人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是在ALVIS认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一声令下 我哪儿都可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像上了战场后再也没回来的女儿一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈惠姐 我们是没有办法获胜的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能用Fafner…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要队长是用普通武器战斗至死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一直在接受训练
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要战斗的是你们的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你支持彗 镝木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论重复多少次都还是这么难过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能将士兵送上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有你 必然无人生还
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也参与了研究开发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用所有本应禁止的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至操作孩子们的基因…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用未成熟的脑来驱动兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会减寿的危险技术 竟普及到了全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军那位叫巴特蓝的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他认真耿直 心中燃烧着使命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是像得可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像年轻时的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉和美羽 给予了我不同于父亲的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽的母亲弓子小姐 对我来说就像是圣母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 太夸张了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您竟然与道生在一起了 真令人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识美羽的爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 代号666
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消灭敌人 为友军带来胜利的野兽之王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最棒的Fafner驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多说一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好弟弟啊 而且是个帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐啊 这个有什么所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城…乙姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要如何祝福世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯 你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水平还不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你之前不也这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不会做歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不是完全不能驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果需要我 可以尽管用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会记着的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你现在更应向后辈们指明一条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会被战斗夺去心和生命的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是痛死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿芹和广登都不知道什么叫手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我来演败将
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当沙包辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下他们也会有勇气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗力增加就能去外面的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打算申请参加派遣部队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐也有一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是L计划的时候 真令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护身符给他们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他们都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟也要上战场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再挂上任何人的照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉色？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是驾驶员的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 只好重新涂装了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡诺恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在努力奋斗以回应期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要去岛外面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令认为他们的提议有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会提前进行新人演习
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要相信人类军？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可是会若无其事攻击我们的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在来的那些人并不憎恨我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道美羽是特别的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定真的能拯救世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派遣部队一定会实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:18:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护美羽 远见学姐也打算去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想跟远见学姐一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想了解外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 奶奶也说说他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双胞胎姐弟想法变得这么不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类并不单纯 有时会变得比敌人更可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此你有所准备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不再是小孩子了 自己决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会反对到底的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美三香 吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始你就是岛的守护神了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃点有力气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零央 有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸以前在一个叫比利时的国家学习工学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里遇到了你妈妈 她是个糕点师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好是那些家伙开始在北极筑巢的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个以狮子徽章而闻名的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字也是取自这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为妈妈希望你能成长为坚强的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我爷爷传下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯 是真刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要老师教过你用法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是拥有狮子魂的武士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Festum见识见识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把你姐姐的头发怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再碰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香奈惠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该我去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我当上驾驶员了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护爸爸妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像姐姐一样 保护这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗 你回房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在公布机体代号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六号机改 「天照」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一号机改 「须佐之男」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五号机改 「月读」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:21:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好记  -帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.87,0:22:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您 卡诺恩老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.91,0:22:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还有什么想知道的尽管问
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需继承和平的时代已远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你即将知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦纷争开始 其将跨越世代绵延不绝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人可知其为何开始 何时结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有为活在当下而战的意志 继续传承
